ong>Boundary Setting</strong></td> +        <td> +          • Scripts for Setting Holiday Boundaries<br /> +          • How to Say No Without Feeling Guilty<br /> +          • Protecting Your Peace During Family Gatherings<br /> +          • Time Limit Strategies for Holiday Events<br /> +          • When Family Doesn't Respect Your Boundaries +        </td> +        <td>High (70K+)</td> +        <td>Low</td> +      </tr> +    </table> + +    <h3>Social Media Viral Strategy</h3> +    <p><strong>TikTok/Instagram Reels Hooks (15-Second Openers):</strong></p> +    <ul> +      <li>\"POV: You're the only one NOT looking forward to the holidays...\"</li> +      <li>\"Things nobody tells you about your first Christmas after divorce...\"</li> +      <li>\"Red flags that your family is toxic af this holiday season...\"</li> +      <li>\"How to survive Thanksgiving with your narcissistic mother-in-law...\"</li> +      <li>\"Me explaining why I'm not attending family Christmas this year...\"</li> +      <li>\"What my therapist told me about holiday obligations...\"</li> +      <li>\"The mug I need for family dinner: [show product]\"</li> +      <li>\"Practicing what I want to say to my ex before the holiday party...\"</li> +      <li>\"Signs you should skip the family gathering this year...\"</li> +      <li>\"My holiday survival kit because therapy is expensive...\"</li> +    </ul> + +    <p><strong>Facebook Post Formulas (High Engagement):</strong></p> +    <ul> +      <li><strong>The Confession:</strong> \"Unpopular opinion: It's okay to skip family holidays if they make you miserable. Here's why...\"</li> +      <li><strong>The Permission Slip:</strong> \"You don't owe anyone your presence during the holidays. Read that again.\"</li> +      <li><strong>The Validation:</strong> \"If the holidays make you anxious instead of joyful, this is for you...\"</li> +      <li><strong>The Humor Approach:</strong> \"Things I wish I could say at family dinner (but my therapist says no)